name: ZipSplitter Part 10 File
summary: An S09 file is the tenth part of a file that was split using ZipSplitter, a program used to split large files into smaller parts. It contains a segment of a larger file, such as an .MP4 or .ZIP file, that is one part of 10 or more other parts. S09 files can be restored, along with the other parts ( .S00 , .S01 , .S02 , etc.) by double-clicking the .EXE file included with the split file(s).
